Lori Kelley is a Singer-Songwriter, and her music is in several different genres. <ref>{{webcite|articleurl=https://www.instagram.com/thelorikelley/|articlename=@thelorikelley|website=Instagram|accessed=1 July 2025}}</ref> She has released two original albums inspired by ''[[The Lord of the Rings]]'': ''A Tale or Two to Tell'' and ''Ladies of the Rings''.
